SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[City], [c0].[Details], [c0].[FirstName], [c0].[IsDeleted], [c0].[LastName], [c0].[MiddleName], [c0].[State], [c0].[StreetAddress], [c0].[ZipCode], [c].[ChildId], [c].[Date], [c].[Id], [c].[IsDeleted], [c].[Notes], [r].[Id], [r].[Email], [r].[FirstName], [r].[IsDeleted], [r].[LastName], [r].[MiddleName], [r].[Phone], [c].[ReporterId], [c].[Status], [c].[UpdateDate]
FROM [Cases] AS [c]
INNER JOIN [Children] AS [c0] ON [c].[ChildId] = [c0].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Reporters] AS [r] ON [c].[ReporterId] = [r].[Id]
